sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant API as DS Pipelines API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant WfPod as Workflow Pod
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant Minio as Minio<br/>9000/TCP S3 API
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Persist as Persistence Agent

    User->>Dashboard: Create Pipeline
    Dashboard->>Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.3
    Proxy->>Proxy: SubjectAccessReview
    Proxy->>API: Forward to 8888/TCP<br/>Bearer Token

    API->>MariaDB: Store Pipeline Metadata<br/>3306/TCP MySQL Auth
    MariaDB-->>API: Success
    API->>Minio: Store Pipeline YAML<br/>9000/TCP AWS SigV4
    Minio-->>API: Artifact Stored
    API-->>Dashboard: Pipeline Created

    User->>Dashboard: Submit Pipeline Run
    Dashboard->>Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward HTTPS
    Proxy->>API: Forward 8888/TCP

    API->>MariaDB: Create Run Record<br/>3306/TCP
    MariaDB-->>API: Run ID
    API->>MLMD: Log Execution Context<br/>8080/TCP gRPC mTLS
    MLMD->>MariaDB: Store ML Metadata<br/>3306/TCP

    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS SA Token
    K8s-->>API: Workflow Created
    API-->>Dashboard: Run Started

    Argo->>K8s: Watch Workflows<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8s-->>Argo: Workflow Event
    Argo->>K8s: Create Workflow Pod<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8s-->>Argo: Pod Created

    WfPod->>Minio: Download Pipeline Artifacts<br/>9000/TCP AWS SigV4
    Minio-->>WfPod: Artifacts
    WfPod->>WfPod: Execute ML Task
    WfPod->>MLMD: Log Artifacts/Metrics<br/>8080/TCP gRPC mTLS
    MLMD->>MariaDB: Store Metadata<br/>3306/TCP
    WfPod->>Minio: Upload Output Artifacts<br/>9000/TCP AWS SigV4
    Minio-->>WfPod: Upload Complete

    WfPod->>API: Report Task Status<br/>8887/TCP gRPC TLS1.3
    API->>MariaDB: Update Run Status<br/>3306/TCP

    Persist->>K8s: Watch Workflow Status<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    K8s-->>Persist: Status Update
    Persist->>MariaDB: Sync Workflow State<br/>3306/TCP MySQL Auth
    MariaDB-->>Persist: Updated

    User->>Dashboard: View Results
    Dashboard->>Route: GET /apis/v1beta1/runs/{id}<br/>Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward HTTPS
    Proxy->>API: Forward 8888/TCP
    API->>MariaDB: Query Run Details<br/>3306/TCP
    MariaDB-->>API: Run Data
    API->>Minio: Generate Pre-signed URL<br/>9000/TCP
    API-->>Dashboard: Run Details + Artifact URLs
    Dashboard-->>User: Results Displayed
